==============
WP-SILCC v1.0
==============

wp-silcc auto-generates tags for blog content.  It uses the OpenSiLCC (http://opensilcc.com) API from SwiftRiver (http://swift.ushahidi.com).  wp-silcc differs from similar auto-tagging plugins because it utilizes active learning techniques to improve it's tagging ability over time.  For more on OpenSiLCC please visit the documentation page here - http://swift.ushahidi.com/doc/doku.php?id=silcc

